---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Important disclaimers regarding financial advice and content."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-12 lg:py-16">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        Important information regarding content on this website.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/20 border-l-2 border-amber-400 pl-4 py-4 mb-8">
        <p class="text-lg m-0">
          <strong>None of the content on this website constitutes financial advice.</strong> All content is for research and educational purposes only.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2>Research Purpose</h2>
      <p>
        This website shares research findings and insights on stablecoins, tokenization, AI, and emerging technologies. Content is intended for academic discourse, not actionable investment guidance.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may contain affiliate links. When present, they are clearly disclosed. I may receive compensation from purchases through these links at no additional cost to you.
      </p>

      <h2>No Warranties</h2>
      <p>
        While I strive for accuracy, no warranties are made regarding completeness or reliability of any content. Information may become outdated without notice.
      </p>

      <h2>Personal Opinions</h2>
      <p>
        All content represents personal opinions and analysis. Views expressed do not necessarily reflect positions of any organizations I may be affiliated with.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions? Email <a href="mailto:info@gokhanturhan.com">info@gokhanturhan.com</a>
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-8">
        Last updated: January 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
